Package frc.robot

Class DriveSwerveSystem

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.DriveSwerveSystem
public class DriveSwerveSystem extends Object
The SwerveDriveSystem is a pseudo static class that implements all functions necessary for a robot Swerve drive.
File: SwerveDriveSystem.java

Referenceable items: (classes)
SwerveDriveSystem.SetSpeedTarget
SwerveDriveSystem.Execute

Depends on:
None -
Operating system specifics:
None - transportable

Notes:
For this to work correctly, the execute method needs to be called every 20 millisecond robot cycle.
